extendedInfo.description: AMS Free Daily Horoscope app offers very personalized horoscope as compared other apps that offer same horoscope for half billion people born in same zodiac sign as you.Your life is unique. So you deserve unique and personalized horoscope. Use this app to get personal horoscope,  which belongs to you only.AMS Free Daily Horoscope app tells you about your * Love life* Health and diseases* Profession and Wealth* Marriage and Family* Education and Luck etc.AMS Free Daily Horoscope app predicts, what can happen in your life in near future and also, what may have happened in recent past.You just need to enter your birth details (date, time and place of birth). Just in case predictions seem to be off, you can try entering birth time, a few minutes later or ahead of given birth time.AMS Free Daily Horoscope app is the most powerful Birth Chart or Vedic Horoscope app based on Indian Astrology / Vedic Astrology / Hindu Astrology / Jyotish.Check your complete horoscopes for today, tomorrow and keep an eye on your horoscope of the week, your monthly horoscope and your yearly horoscope.Please give it a 5 stars rating, if you are satisfied. Otherwise please use Contact Support feature to tell us, how we can improve it. Please don't give bad rating for the issues, which can be resolved.More Features of AMS Free Daily Horoscope app====================================* Predictions are available in English as well as Hindi language* Store multiple horoscopes* Contact Support - in case you need help for using this app.* GPS and Google Maps support for finding birth city* User friendly user interface* Option for sharing this app with friends on Facebook, Twitter, WhatsApp, Email and SMS etc.Download this app now to unlock mysteries of the future.You can also visit http://freedailyhoroscope.in website from your PC, tablet or mobile phone to get free daily horoscope forecasts.Explanation of requested permissions        Your Location: To pre-fill your birth city when creating new horoscope.        Network Communication: To download your horoscope and predictions. Minimal data is transferred to reduce cost of internet usage.        Storage: The information entered in the application will be kept on your phone in order to give you a personalized content every time you open the application.        Phone Calls: Allows you to keep the application open when a phone call or a text message interrupts your reading.        System Tools: Allows the application to run faster when your smartphone is running out of virtual memory.        E-mail Accounts: To pre-fill your email address when you open Contact Support screen.
